folder: Surf Ave. & 20th St. W., Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1) Surf Ave., north side, west from the N.E. corner of West 20th Street, showing in order the Carmen's Sylvia Inn and Restaurant (N.E. corner) and Busoni's Danceland (N.W. corner).

January 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, a closeup of Busoni's Danceland.

January 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
